<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Default Footer</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Use as the site-wide page footer on all public-facing templates. The 4-column layout suits sites with multiple link categories; if fewer than three columns are needed, collapse unused columns rather than leaving them empty. The dark surface creates a clear visual endpoint for the page and ensures the footer never competes with body content above it.</p>
